{"tid":2436093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港接種疫苗再添亡魂　55歲婦打科興後入院亡","createTime":"2021-03-06T21:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T23:41:42.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3af8d9fd554c6d1d51f70006730740568065a2ab","tid":2436093,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:05:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/2OQBRW3AX5APVC5FYMADGMKI4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2F2OQBRW3AX5APVC5FYMADGMKI4E%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=27c27147\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2F2OQBRW3AX5APVC5FYMADGMKI4E%2F&h=a58ff4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/2OQBRW3AX5APVC5FYMADGMKI4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n再多一宗接種科興疫苗後數日內死亡的個案，繼上月底一名有嚴重長期病患的63歲男子接種科興疫苗兩日後死亡，一名55歲女子本周二（2日）在官涌體育館接種科興疫苗，3日後懷疑中風入住廣華醫院，至翌日即今凌晨離世。她是陪同60歲以上人士接種疫苗而可以打針的人士。<br />\n<br />\n該女子3月2日在官涌體育館接種疫苗後，昨晚7時上班期間，突感到左邊身體無力，及後送到明愛醫院治理，發現為腦血管栓塞，再轉送廣華醫院，惟其後情況急劇轉差，至今天凌晨4時送到深切治療部，但不足1小時後離世。衞生署指，該名女子3月5日出現急性中風，轉送廣華醫院接受進一步治理，隨後出現心臟停頓，於今日凌晨不治；衞生署指，接獲呈報後已即時聯絡醫管局，正就事件獲取更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心總監林文健在疫情記者會指，就事件代表政府對患者家屬致以深切慰問，但指暫時未能確定事件與接種疫苗有關。"},{"pid":"d44e06431f8f439e2fdb1162ca2c6db59513132f","tid":2436093,"uid":361247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"又多2球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b6d24de215a50f124c017f595f6cd8f8a756ac","tid":2436093,"uid":98172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44e06431f8f439e2fdb1162ca2c6db59513132f","tid":2436093,"uid":361247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"又多2球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:30:07.000Z","msg":"上次死左人都走數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2f27546ad39d0cd7082b8e73a4b938be839b62","tid":2436093,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44e06431f8f439e2fdb1162ca2c6db59513132f","tid":2436093,"uid":361247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"又多2球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:34:24.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66984e289a18ce856a4000b2db21caad356e46d6","tid":2436093,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:47:16.000Z","msg":"8日死2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58067ee3c072dc873fe540742e214829ef1cfd4d","tid":2436093,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:41:42.000Z","msg":"個呀嬸實收左錢想抹黑政府<br />\n我地藍朋友唔會信架<br />\n中國人一定打中國苗，非科興不打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}